  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "driver cum manager",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a <strong>Driver cum Restaurant Manager</strong> to support our restaurant operations and daily logistics.</p><h3>Job Responsibilities</h3><p><strong>Driving & Logistics</strong></p><ul><li><p>Drive company vehicle to purchase ingredients, supplies, and equipment</p></li><li><p>Deliver food, documents, or items between outlets when required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Operations & Management</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist in daily restaurant operations and supervision</p></li><li><p>Open and close the restaurant when assigned</p></li><li><p>Monitor staff attendance, discipline, and work performance</p></li><li><p>Coordinate staff schedules and support manpower arrangements</p></li><li><p>Handle basic purchasing, stock checking, and inventory control</p></li></ul><p><strong>Customer & Outlet Support</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle customer enquiries and resolve complaints professionally</p></li><li><p>Support front-of-house or kitchen operations when required</p></li><li><p>Ensure cleanliness, hygiene, and food safety standards are followed</p></li><li><p>Assist in events, catering, or special functions when needed</p></li></ul><p><strong>Administrative Duties</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepare simple daily reports (sales, staff attendance, inventory)</p></li><li><p>Liaise with suppliers, management, and external parties</p></li><li><p>Carry out any other duties assigned by management</p></li></ul><h3>Job Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Valid Singapore driving licence (Class 3 or relevant)</p></li><li><p>Experience in F&B or restaurant operations preferred</p></li><li><p>Responsible, honest, and able to multitask</p></li><li><p>Willing to work flexible hours, including weekends and public holidays</p></li><li><p>Good communication and basic management skills</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and handle pressure</p></li></ul>",
